scenarios.name: Scenario 1
scenarios.description: Current mitigation measures are completely lifted in 2 weeks without replacement.

scenarios.name: Scenario 2
scenarios.description: Current mitigation measures stay in for 4 weeks and are replaced by milder measures afterwards.

scenarios.name: Scenario 3
scenarios.description: Current mitigation measures stay in for 2 weeks and are replaced by strong mitigation afterwards.

scenarios.name: Scenario 4
scenarios.description: Current mitigation measures stay in for 2 weeks and are replaced by moderate mitigation afterwards.
